  {
    
    "name": "Section 3",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-612933882630636112 gps gpsi",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/s3x280-0x/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_STATIC&editorId=612933882546750032&sectionId=612933882630636112)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"off_lazy_script"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCPo2QyNVg_text","label":"ggCPo2QyNVg_text","default":"<p><strong>\"What you're dealing with isn't just aging,\" Dr. Reynolds said.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>He pulled up a simple diagram on his screen and turned it toward me.</p><p>\"It's a compression problem. And almost no one is talking about it.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>He pointed to a small gland sitting right next to a cluster of nerves.</p><p>\"This is your prostate. And this,\" he traced the nerve bundle running alongside it, \"is the pathway that carries every arousal signal from your brain to your penis.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>He kept going.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>\"When your prostate swells, it presses directly against those nerves. The signal your brain sends gets weaker. Distorted. By the time it arrives, it's not strong enough to do its job.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>\"So the erection problems aren't starting in the penis?\" I asked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>\"No. They're starting here.\" He tapped the prostate on the diagram. \"And every month the swelling continues, the signal gets quieter.\"</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>I sat back in my chair.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Two years of declining erections. Six months on pills that kept needing higher doses. And no one had ever shown me this.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>\"So what fixes it?\" I asked.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>He paused.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>\"That's the part the system isn't built to tell you.\"</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg6WshnvRMq_text","label":"gg6WshnvRMq_text","default":"<p><i><strong>\"You're not losing function because you're getting older. You're losing function because something is pressing on the nerve that controls it.\"</strong></i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggB_erNDX8J_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggB_erNDX8J_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_x4i5pmx4i5pmx4i5_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYz_YaWLs-_text","label":"ggYz_YaWLs-_text","default":"<p><strong>I felt everything shift.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Two years of pills next to my nightstand. Two years of watching my wife's expression change from desire to something that looked like patience.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Two years of telling myself this was just how it was now.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And it had a cause. A physical, specific, fixable cause.</p><p>\"So what do I do about it?\" I whispered.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggrYuayZNc0_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggrYuayZNc0_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/sad_as.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggJi4ibQV97_text","label":"ggJi4ibQV97_text","default":"<strong>Here's How MeridEase Labs Fixes All 5 Problems at Once:</strong>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_SylVG7-I_text","label":"gg_SylVG7-I_text","default":"1. Lifts the Pressure Off the Nerve That Controls Erections"},{"type":"html","id":"gg5PjsAdd7Z_text","label":"gg5PjsAdd7Z_text","default":"<p>Pills force blood in. That is all they do.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They do nothing about the swollen prostate pressing against the nerve that controls the whole response. So the pills keep needing higher doses. And the real problem keeps getting worse.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>MeridEase Labs contains cold-pressed pumpkin seed oil with intact beta-sitosterol.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Beta-sitosterol reduces prostate swelling at the tissue level. The pressure lifts. The nerve signal travels fully again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Beta-sitosterol from cold-pressed pumpkin seed oil is the only compound in peer-reviewed research shown to reduce prostate swelling while directly restoring nerve function.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Most pumpkin seed oil products use high-heat extraction. Heat destroys beta-sitosterol completely. You end up with oil that does nothing.</p><p>MeridEase Labs cold-presses below 40 degrees Celsius. The beta-sitosterol survives intact. It reaches prostate tissue. It works.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>\"Tried two other brands for months. Nothing changed. Week three on MeridEase Labs and things were actually working again.\"</i> <i>-- David M.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg_retYyIky_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg_retYyIky_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_yvnpw3yvnpw3yvnp.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwg5NyrzOE_text","label":"ggwg5NyrzOE_text","default":"2. Stops the Root Cause From Growing Back"},{"type":"html","id":"gg1oHzIF6mE_text","label":"gg1oHzIF6mE_text","default":"<p>The reason the prostate keeps swelling is a hormone called DHT.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Your body converts testosterone into DHT as you age. DHT builds up in prostate tissue and drives it to expand. If you shrink the prostate without stopping DHT, it grows right back.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>MeridEase Labs includes standardized saw palmetto extract that blocks the enzyme that converts testosterone into DHT.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The prostate stops growing. The shrinkage holds. The nerve stays clear.</p><p><strong>Standardized saw palmetto is the only extract clinically proven to inhibit DHT conversion at a level that produces real, lasting results.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Most saw palmetto products use cheap underdosed powder. Not enough fatty acids to move the needle. The clinical studies used concentrated standardized extracts. Most supplements on the market do not come close to that threshold.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>\"My doctor said my prostate had reduced in size. He asked what I changed. He actually wrote it down.\"</i> <i>-- Roger T.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg465JXgm2y_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"gg465JXgm2y_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_5oh8go5oh8go5oh8.jpg"},{"type":"html","id":"gg3gSe63GPU_text","label":"gg3gSe63GPU_text","default":"3. Restores the Full Nerve Signal to the Penis"},{"type":"html","id":"gg2nYlyqUhz_text","label":"gg2nYlyqUhz_text","default":"<p>Compression is not the only problem.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>When the prostate stays swollen long enough, inflammation builds around the nerve bundle. That inflammation damages the nerve over time. The signal gets quieter every month.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>This is why pills stop working. They force blood flow. But the nerve telling the body to respond keeps breaking down underneath.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>MeridEase Labs reduces the inflammation around the nerve bundle.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Nerve sensitivity recovers. The signal strengthens. Morning erections return. Spontaneous response comes back on its own.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>\"Morning wood returned in week two. I laughed out loud. My wife thought something was wrong.\"</i> <i>-- Ryan Hudson</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggDY7n9xHEY_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggDY7n9xHEY_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_6qy0cd6qy0cd6qy0_1.png"},{"type":"html","id":"ggxyIW-q1-e_label","label":"ggxyIW-q1-e_label","default":"<p>CLICK HERE TO CHECK AVAILABILITY</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggamC8gEgTZ_text","label":"ggamC8gEgTZ_text","default":"4. Rebuilds Natural Blood Flow From the Inside"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIbn3Oq_wA_text","label":"ggIbn3Oq_wA_text","default":"<p>Even after the nerve signal restores, the blood vessels need to respond.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Chronic prostate inflammation damages the cells lining the penile arteries. Those cells produce nitric oxide. Nitric oxide is what tells the vessels to open and let blood fill the erectile chambers. Without it, everything downstream stalls.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>The antioxidants in MeridEase Labs cold-pressed oil protect and repair those cells.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Nitric oxide production rebuilds. Vessels dilate fully. Blood fills properly. Not forced. Restored.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><i>\"By week six I needed nothing. No pills. Just my body working the way it did ten years ago. I didn't think that was possible anymore.\"</i> <i>-- Mark S.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggq9UBVMipI_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggq9UBVMipI_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0809/8739/0192/files/Gemini_Generated_Image_jh7z5ujh7z5ujh7z_1.png"}],
